ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] And another bites the dust...
ygData.msgSnippet: Wow, I never thought you would pass from this world afore me Gil.  Adieu, adieu.  May yours steps always be light with song wherever thou travels. Kitasi
ygData.messageBody:
Wow, I never thought you would pass from this world afore me Gil. Adieu,
adieu. May yours steps always be light with song wherever thou travels.

Kitasi Faegehearper
